title: KICKSTART YOUR FITNESS JOURNEY! 15-Min Beginner Interval Treadmill Follow Along!
description:
We have an awesome beginner interval workout for you today! Let's get sweaty!

15 minutes of run and recovery intervals

All speeds and inclines are suggestions. Please stay safe and within your comfort zone!

Join this channel to get access to perks:

03:35 - Workout!
13:35 - Cool Down
